										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Time-consuming. Thatâ€™s one way to describe posting to social media, reviewing analytics for each platform, and handling other aspects of social media marketing manually. No wonder social media management tools are in such high demand.</p>
<p>But with so many to choose fromâ€”and some with hefty price tagsâ€”you may struggle to figure out which tools are both good and affordable. This list will end that struggle, breaking down both the zero-cost features of the best free social media management tools and their paid options.</p>
<h2>Best free social media management tools</h2>
<ol>
<li><a href="#buffer">Buffer</a></li>
<li><a href="#friends">Friends+Me</a></li>
